      <div class="text-black px-10 p-text lg:max-w-xl">
        <p class="pb-5">
          Embark on your journey to becoming a Commercial Pilot with the unwavering support of Ideal Aviation. Whether you're a flying enthusiast looking to turn your passion into a career or a dedicated individual aspiring to enter the aviation industry, we've got you covered every step of the way. Our program seamlessly integrates comprehensive theoretical instruction with immersive hands-on flight training, ensuring you're equipped with the skills to confidently operate and navigate aircraft while adhering to the highest professional standards.
        </p>
        <p class="pb-5">
          <span class="font-bold font-sans text-2xl">Choose Ideal Aviation and Start Your Commercial Pilot Training Today</span>
        </p>
        <p class="pb-5">
          Soar with Ideal Aviation's Commercial Pilot Certificate! Command aircraft for pay, transporting passengers, cargo, and undertaking diverse missions. From private pilot to commercial heights, our guidance propels your journey to new altitudes. Our experienced certified flight instructors (CFII) will help you become a better and safer pilot.
        </p>
        <p class="grid place-items-center pb-10">
          <%= link_to "CONTACT US",  contact_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-primary"%>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
      <%= image_tag "commercial-instructor.webp", alt: "Pilot Instructor smiling beside the plane", class: ""%>
    </div>
